    <item>
      <title>从长远来看，我们的预测都是经过修订的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-11-22/2025-forecasts-in-the-long-run-we-re-all-just-revised-projections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[每年都会发布明年的预测，然后将其分解，这是一项例行公事。接下来是长期预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-11-22/2025-forecasts-in-the-long-run-we-re-all-just-revised-projections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 05:01:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受能源制裁影响，俄罗斯巨型液化天然气建设设施灯光昏暗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/russia-energy-sanctions-hit-novatek-s-arctic-lng-construction-facility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯唯一的液化天然气模块建造厂的活动似乎已经下滑，这再次表明西方的制裁正在阻碍俄罗斯成为这一关键能源市场主要参与者的雄心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/russia-energy-sanctions-hit-novatek-s-arctic-lng-construction-facility</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
